---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Case Studies - Lumina Consulting"
  description="See how we've helped companies transform their data into strategic insights and automate key processes."
  lang="en"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative py-24 bg-lum-black overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute top-1/4 -right-32 w-96 h-96 bg-lum-coral/15 rounded-full blur-3xl" />
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 -left-32 w-96 h-96 bg-lum-coral/10 rounded-full blur-3xl" />
    </div>
    <div class="container-custom relative">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <span class="badge bg-white/10 text-white border-white/20 mb-6">Testimonials</span>
        <h1 class="text-white mb-6">Case Studies</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-lum-slate-light max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Real results from companies that transformed their operations with Lumina Consulting
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Case 1: Automotive Network -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="mb-10 scroll-fade">
          <span class="badge-accent mb-4">Case Study</span>
          <h2 class="mb-2">Quality Control Automation and Price Analysis</h2>
          <p class="text-lum-slate">Automotive Dealership Network</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-10">
          <!-- Challenge -->
          <div class="card scroll-fade">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-red-50 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg">The Challenge</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-lum-slate text-sm">
              An automotive dealership network published dozens of vehicles daily but had no way to detect incomplete listings or compare their prices with the market.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Solution -->
          <div class="card scroll-fade animation-delay-100">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-lum-coral/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lum-coral" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg">Our Solution</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-lum-slate text-sm">
              Automated system that scans listings, detects errors, compares prices with competitors, and sends daily reports via email.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Results -->
          <div class="card scroll-fade animation-delay-200">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-lum-success/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lum-success" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg">Results</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class="text-lum-slate text-sm space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-lum-success flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                Reduction in incomplete listings
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-lum-success flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                Faster pricing decisions
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Testimonial -->
        <div class="testimonial-card scroll-fade animation-delay-300">
          <p class="text-lg text-lum-slate mb-4">
            "Before, we had to review everything by hand, and errors still slipped through. Now every morning we receive a summary with cars missing photos, prices that are off-market, and clear recommendations. It's like having an analyst working 24/7 for us."
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-lum-black">
            — Commercial Manager, Automotive Dealership Network
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider-gradient" />

  <!-- Case 2: Veterinary Clinic -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="mb-10 scroll-fade">
          <span class="badge-accent mb-4">Case Study</span>
          <h2 class="mb-2">Financial and Operational Visibility</h2>
          <p class="text-lum-slate">Veterinary Clinic Network</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-10">
          <!-- Challenge -->
          <div class="card scroll-fade">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-red-50 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg">The Challenge</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-lum-slate text-sm">
              An expanding veterinary clinic had no clear view of financial performance. Information was scattered across multiple files with no strategic reporting.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Solution -->
          <div class="card scroll-fade animation-delay-100">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-lum-coral/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lum-coral" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg">Our Solution</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-lum-slate text-sm">
              Automated system that extracts data from their management system, processes it with Power Query, and generates visual reports with clear performance visibility.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Results -->
          <div class="card scroll-fade animation-delay-200">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-lum-success/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lum-success" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg">Results</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class="text-lum-slate text-sm space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-lum-success flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                Data consolidated in one file
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-lum-success flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                Better control of revenue and cash flows
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Testimonial -->
        <div class="testimonial-card scroll-fade animation-delay-300">
          <p class="text-lg text-lum-slate mb-4">
            "We had the data, but not the complete picture. Now we can see how each section of the clinic is performing, how much we're generating, and which areas need improvement. It gave us the professionalism boost we needed to grow."
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-lum-black">
            — Director, Veterinary Clinic Network
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-lum-black relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-lum-coral/10 rounded-full blur-3xl" />
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-lum-coral/10 rounded-full blur-3xl" />
    </div>
    <div class="container-custom relative">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-white mb-6 scroll-fade">Could your company be the next success story?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-lum-slate-light mb-10 scroll-fade animation-delay-100">
          Let's discuss your business's specific challenges
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center scroll-fade animation-delay-200">
          <a
            href="https://wa.me/56991629095?text=Hi,%20I'm%20interested%20in%20learning%20more%20about%20Lumina%20Consulting's%20services"
            target="_blank"
            class="btn-primary"
          >
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/>
            </svg>
            Contact via WhatsApp
          </a>
          <a href="/en/contact" class="btn-secondary bg-white/5 border-white/20 text-white hover:bg-white/10">
            Request Free Assessment
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
